Package com.BSTree

Interface BSTree<T>

Type Parameters:
T - a structure representing single node
All Known Implementing Classes:
BinarySearchTree
public interface BSTree<T>
Generic interface with declarations of methods common for binary search trees. Binary Search Tree is a Binary Tree, where nodes with bigger value are being placed to the right of the parent node, and nodes with lower values are being placed to the left of the parent node.
